<h2 class="text-center">Welcome to Linkshare</h2>
<iframe src="~/index.html" style="width:960px;height:360px;max-width:100%;
                                  overflow:hidden;border:none;padding:0;margin:0 auto;
                                  display:block; margin-bottom:20px;"
                                  marginheight="0" marginwidth="0">
</iframe>
<div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="panel panel-primary">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h3 class="panel-title">About Portal</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body home-msgbox">
            <p>
                This is a portal all about sharing links. You can browse currently
                submitted links to see if you can find anything interesting.
            </p>
            <p>
                Do you have a link to share? Then @Html.ActionLink(
                    "Register Here",
                    "Index",
                    new { Controller = "Register", Area = "Security" }) and share it.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="panel panel-primary">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h3 class="panel-title">Technologies Used</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body home-msgbox">
            <p>
                This portal is purely developed on 3-layered architecture in VS2013 using
                the following technologies: Asp.Net MVC, jQuery, BootStrap, C#.Net,
                Entity Framework and MS SQL Server.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="col-md-4">
    <div class="panel panel-primary">
        <div class="panel-heading">
            <h3 class="panel-title">Real About</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-body home-msgbox">
            <p>
                This site was created as an example of using ASP.NET MVC with a 3 tier
                architecture approach.
            </p>
            <p>
                Feel free to browse around or explore the code which is also available
                on my <a href="http://github.com/rwhiten/">github page</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>